text: cyCONDOR provide integrated function prepare condor object starting .fcs files .csv files. files saved single directory FCSpath, user now also define number events process file setting ‘ceil’. load .csv files instead .fcs useCSV setting set TRUE. data transformation cyCONDOR provide different options inherited form Cytofkit package (Chen et al. 2016). transformation can set : - y: CyTOF data - f: FlowCytometry data (fixed logicle transform) - c: CITE-seq data (clr transformtation) - : FlowCytometry data (recommended, auto-logicle transformation) used can also decide step remove unwanted parameters important downstream analysis (e.g. Time). Last important piece build condor object metadata table. supplied .csv file one column matching name .fcs .csv files. column matching file names stated ‘filename_col’.
